title: 2020 Week 11 Preview
itunes:title: 2020 Week 11 Preview
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal preview each of the upcoming week 11 games starting with the two primetime games between the Chiefs and Raiders (2:45) and the Bucs-Raiders (7:58). Gregg has the first overall pick for the rest of the games and chooses the Falcons-Saints rivalry (13:07) and Dan is psyched about the Titans-Ravens game falling to him (23:05). Marc is in love with the Dolphins (38:19) and we break down the most important thing of Week 11- Justin Herberts haircut (1:04:32)

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
